Lets motivate each other and do only what works for our bodies 💪❤️

My day 1 went very well and it pushed to have a stressful and successful Day 2✨️

Stick and follow along to share our journies together 💕

Day 1 /75

115g protein and 1600 calories 💪 

I am starting a new challenge to see how consistent I am with myself. This challenge is for 75 days.  No its not the regular 75 hard. Because I am doing this challenge at my own comfort.

My rules are simple:

Drink 3 to 4 liters of water
Be productive with work
Try to avoid procrastination 
Be active ( either with gym or walking for 45 mins to 1 hour)
Read 5 to 10 pages of book 
No sugar
Eat only how much my body needs
Eat atleast 80 to 120 g protein everyday

I dont know if I can do this, but I will put my 100% No matter what. I am posting my journey every single day and let's motivate each other with our goals❤️
